OL,3,CMassive council shake-up for Kent,
OL,4,CSussex and Oxfordshire
OL,6,FHundreds of thousands of residents
OL,7,Fwill see their local authorities
OL,8,Fdissolved as the government confirms
OL,9,Fsweeping reforms across the ITV
OL,10,FMeridian region.
OL,12,FThe political map of the South East is
OL,13,Fset for its most dramatic
OL,14,Ftransformation in fifty years, after
OL,15,Fministers confirmed major
OL,16,Freorganisations for Kent, Sussex,
OL,17,FOxfordshire, and West Berkshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
