FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784281688
OL,3,CMassive council shake-up for Kent,
OL,4,CSussex and Oxfordshire
OL,6,FUnder the sweeping plans, complex "two-
OL,7,Ftier" council systems will be
OL,8,Fabolished in favour of streamlined
OL,9,F"unitary" authorities.
OL,11,FThese new super-councils will take
OL,12,Fover all local duties, meaning
OL,13,Feverything from social care and road
OL,14,Frepairs to bin collections and
OL,15,Fplanning permission will be managed
OL,16,Funder one single roof.
OL,18,FKent and Medway: 14 Councils Replaced
OL,19,Fby Four New Authorities
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784281688
OL,3,CMassive council shake-up for Kent,
OL,4,CSussex and Oxfordshire
OL,6,FIn Kent's biggest local government
OL,7,Fshake-up in half a century, the
OL,8,Fgovernment is completely scrapping
OL,9,FKent County Council, Medway Council,
OL,10,Fand all twelve of the county's
OL,11,Fdistrict, borough, and city councils.
OL,13,FFollowing a public consultation that
OL,14,Fdrew around 3,000 responses, the
OL,15,FSecretary of State has decided to
OL,16,Fdivide the county into four brand-new
OL,17,Funitary councils:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784281688
OL,3,CMassive council shake-up for Kent,
OL,4,CSussex and Oxfordshire
OL,6,FThe decision was not the first choice
OL,7,Ffor all local leaders. Cllr Jim
OL,8,FMartin, Leader of Folkestone & Hythe
OL,9,FDistrict Council, admitted: "Although
OL,10,Fthis was not the option for local
OL,11,Fgovernment in Kent that I and fellow
OL,12,Fcouncillors supported, we shall be
OL,13,Fendeavouring to ensure that the
OL,14,Freorganisation is carried out so that
OL,15,Fwe continue to deliver the very best
OL,16,Fservices for residents."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784281688
OL,3,CMassive council shake-up for Kent,
OL,4,CSussex and Oxfordshire
OL,6,FIn a joint statement, Kent and
OL,7,FMedway's council leaders said: "We
OL,8,Fwant to reassure our residents that
OL,9,Fnot one of our services will change
OL,10,Fovernight ` you will still be dealing
OL,11,Fwith the same council staff tomorrow
OL,12,Fand the day after that.
OL,14,F"The new councils will not come into
OL,15,Fbeing until 1 April 2028. Our focus
OL,16,Fwill be supporting our staff through
OL,17,Fthis change while helping them to
OL,18,Fcarry on delivering our business-as-
OL,19,Fusual services seamlessly."
OL,21,FSussex: Brighton Expands Eastward
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784281688
OL,3,CMassive council shake-up for Kent,
OL,4,CSussex and Oxfordshire
OL,6,FIn East Sussex, the existing seven
OL,7,Fcouncils will be replaced by just two
OL,8,Funitary authorities.
OL,10,FBrighton and Hove City Council, which
OL,11,Fis already a unitary authority, will
OL,12,Fexpand its borders eastward, absorbing
OL,13,Ffour coastal wards currently managed
OL,14,Fby Lewes District and East Sussex
OL,15,FCounty councils.
OL,17,FWhile East Sussex's path is clear,
OL,18,Fplans for West Sussex have been put on
OL,19,Fice. Communities Secretary Steve Reed
OL,20,Ftold Parliament that "further time is
OL,21,Frequired to get the decision right."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784281688
OL,3,CMassive council shake-up for Kent,
OL,4,CSussex and Oxfordshire
OL,6,FThe delay was welcomed by Andrew
OL,7,FGriffith, Conservative MP for Arundel
OL,8,Fand South Downs, who had strongly
OL,9,Fopposed the plans: "I welcome that as
OL,10,Fa result of opposition from myself and
OL,11,Fothers, the government has at least
OL,12,Fpostponed the breakup of West Sussex
OL,13,Ftoday. This whole proposal was costly
OL,14,Fand an unnecessary distraction and
OL,15,Fshould now be shelved entirely."
OL,17,FThe government remains committed to
OL,18,Fimplementing the Sussex changes by
OL,19,FApril 2028, with transitional
OL,20,Felections scheduled for May 2027.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784281688
OL,3,CMassive council shake-up for Kent,
OL,4,CSussex and Oxfordshire
OL,6,FOxfordshire & West Berkshire: Seven
OL,7,FCouncils Replaced by Three
OL,9,FThe government has confirmed that
OL,10,FOxfordshire and West Berkshire's seven
OL,11,Fexisting councils will also be
OL,12,Fdissolved and replaced by three brand-
OL,13,Fnew unitary councils starting 1 April
OL,14,F2028:
OL,16,FThe decision has met immediate
OL,17,Fresistance from local leaders who had
OL,18,Fcampaigned for a two-council model
OL,19,Finstead.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784281688
OL,3,CMassive council shake-up for Kent,
OL,4,CSussex and Oxfordshire
OL,6,FCllr Maggie Filipova-Rivers, Leader of
OL,7,FSouth Oxfordshire District Council,
OL,8,Fcalled the three-unitary decision
OL,9,F"deeply disappointing": "Creating
OL,10,Fthree new authorities risks additional
OL,11,Fcomplexity, duplicated costs and
OL,12,Freduced economies of scale.
OL,14,F"We are especially concerned for those
OL,15,Frural communities that will now be
OL,16,Fbrought into a unitary authority
OL,17,Fdominated by Oxford City. This will
OL,18,Fimpact over 21,000 residents across
OL,19,Fsome 25 villages including
OL,20,FBerinsfield, Garsington, and Wheatley."
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
