OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784281688
OL,3,CMassive council shake-up for Kent,
OL,4,CSussex and Oxfordshire
OL,6,FFor residents across Kent, Sussex,
OL,7,FOxfordshire, and West Berkshire, daily
OL,8,Fservices will continue as normal for
OL,9,Fnow.
OL,11,FFollowing public consultations, the
OL,12,Fexisting local councils in all
OL,13,Faffected areas will spend the next two
OL,14,Fyears working on complex transition
OL,15,Fplans.
OL,17,FThe brand-new super-councils are
OL,18,Fscheduled to officially take power on
OL,19,F1 April 2028.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
